node.text:
@onbeatman 
has created this incredible homage to the Top Gun series. Go give him a follow and get him to 3k followers! 

WATCH THE 4k UHD trailer on YouTube.com/OnBeatMan 

"After months of painstaking work… I recreated the TOP GUN:  MAVERICK  trailer in Lego, one frame at a time.  This was created 100% independently out of my love for Top Gun, cinema, and LEGO. 
Special Thanks to those who helped with this project! In OP post.
 
#lego #legophotography #legoarmy #legonavy #legowar #legomania #legotopgun #topgun #topgunmaverick #brickfilm #animation #stopmotion #onbeatman #legocinema #blender #blenderrender #aftereffects #tomcruise  #legomoc  #legofighterjet #legoairplane #legoairport #f14tomcat #f14 #legomluntain #fighterjet #airplane #airplanes 
@paramountpics @topgunmovie
